    text: "Builders and developers often email detailed plastering specs — room counts, surface types, fire-rating requirements, programme schedules. The AI confirms receipt and packages the details so you can review and respond with a proper quote."
  },
  {
    icon: '⏰',
    title: 'Out-of-Hours Coverage',
    text: "Emails arrive at all hours — a letting agent at 6pm, a homeowner at midnight. Without AI Email, those sit unanswered until you check your inbox between jobs. With it, every sender gets immediate confirmation."
