  scenario="It is Thursday at 4:15pm. A project manager for a regional housebuilder emails your business: 'We are looking for plastering contractors for phase 2 of a 24-unit development in Warrington. Full skim to all walls and ceilings, standard spec, starting March. Could you provide a day rate and confirm your availability?' You are on site finishing a domestic job and will not check email until tomorrow. Without AI Email, the project manager does not hear anything until Friday afternoon — by which time three other plasterers have already confirmed interest. With AI Email Response, they receive an instant reply: 'Thank you for your enquiry regarding the Warrington project. We have received the details and will review the specification and respond with availability and rates. If you would like to discuss further in the meantime, please call us on [number].' You review the email Sunday evening and submit your rates Monday morning — first in the queue."
